Fleece fabric:? Microfleece fabrication helps retain and evenly distribute warmth for midlayer or outer layer wear.? Moisture-wicking design moves perspiration away from the skin to dry on the surface.? Gathered ruching accents the curved princess seams.? 100 g fabric weight.
Contrast stitching sets off the pieced, zig-zag design.
Quarter-zip closure with zipper garage and inner draft flap.
